N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 ยง 22.9 - Delivery of certificates

State Regulations

Certificates of literacy shall be delivered in person or
mailed as soon as practicable after the close of the examination to all
applicants who pass the New York State Regents literacy test. Notes
